                "invention-title": [
                    "Technical method for preparing lithium carbonate and titanium dioxide from lithium titanate",
                    "一种钛酸锂制备碳酸锂和二氧化钛的技术方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a technical method for preparing lithium carbonate and titanium dioxide from lithium titanate. The preparation method comprises the following steps: firstly, stirring and mixing powder forms of lithium titanate (Li4Ti5O12), ferric phosphate (FePO4) and glucose (C6H12O6) in proportion by a dry method to obtain a precursor, and calcining the precursor in an inert environment at 600-800 DEG C for 3-8 hours to obtain a mixed product of lithium iron phosphate (LiFePO4) and titanium dioxide (TiO2); and dissolving the calcined product with sulfuric acid, and finally controlling the pH value to be 1.5-2. And filtering and separating to obtain a filtrate which is a mixed solution containing lithium, phosphorus and iron and a filter cake which is insoluble substance titanium dioxide, and washing and drying the titanium dioxide filter cake to obtain a titanium dioxide product. Adding an oxidizing agent hydrogen peroxide and a precipitating agent sodium carbonate into the filtrate to obtain an iron phosphate and lithium sulfate solution, wherein the concentration of lithium in the solution is controlled to be 10-15g/L; the lithium sulfate is added with a sodium carbonate lithium precipitation agent to obtain a lithium carbonate product after pH adjustment and impurity removal, and the lithium recovery rate reaches 95% or above."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种钛酸锂制备碳酸锂和二氧化钛的技术方法。其制备过程是：按比例先将钛酸锂（Li4Ti5O12）、磷酸铁（FePO4）和葡萄糖（C6H12O6）的粉末形态干法搅拌混合得到前驱体，置于惰性环境下600~800℃煅烧3~8h，得到磷酸铁锂（LiFePO4）和二氧化钛（TiO2）的混合产物。将煅烧产物采用通过硫酸溶解，最终pH控制1.5~2。过滤分离后，滤液为含锂、磷、铁的混合溶液，滤饼为不溶物二氧化钛，二氧化钛滤饼洗涤烘干后得到二氧化钛产品。滤液加入氧化剂双氧水和沉淀剂碳酸钠得到磷酸铁和硫酸锂溶液，溶液锂浓度控制10~15g/L。硫酸锂再通过调节pH除杂后加入碳酸钠沉锂剂得到碳酸锂产品，锂回收率达到95%以上。"
                }
